{"tid":219993,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】時鐘機關之星【第 4 話】","createTime":"2017-04-27T15:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T02:16:31.000Z","uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c6365571e482357e2c3ff4fbd726cd939bebe7","tid":219993,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/cp/img/main_visual.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2Fanime%2Fcp%2Fimg%2Fmain_visual.png&h=76bf689b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時鐘機關之星<br />\nクロックワーク・プラネット<br />\nClockWork Planet<br />\n<br />\n雖然很突然，但是世界早就已經滅亡了。已經死亡的地球上的一切，變成一切都是用齒輪與發條加以重現、再度建構的世界─「時鐘機關之星」。高中生 見浦直人是個成績吊車尾的高中生，某天突然有個黑色箱子墜落在他家，箱子裡頭是一具自動人偶少女 琉紫，於是兩人的邂逅轉動了命運的齒輪。<br />\n<br />\nPV2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r8AhkWM9uNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr8AhkWM9uNs&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=af6b4a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r8AhkWM9uNs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n──STAFF── <br />\n原作：榎宮祐、暇奈椿 <br />\n角色原案：茨乃 <br />\n監督：長澤剛 <br />\n系列構成：杉原研二 <br />\n角色設計：島村秀一 <br />\n機械設計：寺岡賢司 <br />\n道具設計：原由知 <br />\n世界觀設定：末武康光、枝松聖 <br />\n美術設計：久保田正宏 <br />\n美術監督：甲斐政俊 <br />\n色彩設定：水野多恵子 <br />\n3DCG：船越勇貴 <br />\n攝影監督：武原健二 <br />\n編集：松村正宏 <br />\n音響監督：本山哲 <br />\n音樂：兼松 眾、中村巴奈重、中野香梨、寶野聡史 <br />\n動畫製作：XEBEC<br />\n<br />\n──CAST──<br />\n見浦 直人：南條愛乃<br />\n琉紫：加隈亜衣<br />\n瑪麗&middot;蓓爾&middot;布列格：大西沙織<br />\n瓦伊尼&middot;哈爾達：松田健一郎<br />\n昂克兒：千本木彩花<br />\n<br />\n──放送──<br />\nTBS 木曜 深夜1時58分〜<br />\n<br />\n──回帶──<br />\n立即重溫繁體中文字幕 第 1 至 3 話 ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ebb.io/anime/138x187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Febb.io%2Fanime%2F138x187&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=bc56ab17\" target=\"_blank\">https://ebb.io/anime/138x187</a><br />\n<br />\n──官方網站──<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/cp/onair/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2Fanime%2Fcp%2Fonair%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1479d2bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/cp/onair/</a>"},{"pid":"b5d6bbf6c28dc69b9259866fba554288572ac93f","tid":219993,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"GCF9"},{"pid":"9be757a74c5332464cb855203b2d5659a5d59434","tid":219993,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GCF9</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6183b234069c90c3b96757efeb1f82cad7d1184","tid":219993,"uid":2345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:48:05.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"febeeb66fa147e9066feb94239c515a27f641dfb","tid":219993,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e7cc9c84bd7578775b6682e914f8d9723eaf9b","tid":219993,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"是來聽OP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db84b1b0734b9dffc1675a3eb728009064298ac","tid":219993,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"到底比左幾多錢畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0fa31f89195563f4f9307683e035a84d13ab89","tid":219993,"uid":476,"like":0,"disl